{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 70,
  "title": "第七十章（懷玉）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "吾言甚易知也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "甚易行也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "而人莫之能知也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "而莫之能行也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "言有君。"
    },
    {
      "text": "事有宗。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯无知也，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以不我知。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知我者希，則我貴矣。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人被褐而懷玉。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人惡柔弱，好剛強也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我所言有宗祖根本，事有君臣上下，世人不知者，非我之無德，不與我反也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫惟聖人也，是我德之暗，不見於外，窮極微妙，故無知也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "希，少也。唯達道者乃能知我，故為貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "被褐者薄外，懷玉者厚內，匿寶藏德，不以示人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 7,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "可不出戶窺牖而知，故曰甚易知也。無為而成，故曰甚易行也。惑於躁欲，故曰，莫之能知也。迷於榮利，故曰，莫之能行也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 6,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "宗，萬物之宗也。君，萬物之主也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以其言有宗、事有君之故，故有知之人不得不知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯深，故知者希也；知我益希，我亦無匹。故曰，知我者希則我者貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "被褐者，同其塵，懷玉者，寶其真也。聖人之所以難知，以其同塵而不殊，懷玉而不渝，故難知而為貴也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
